body:
I have a [CL](https://go-review.googlesource.com/#/c/27932/) that needs some updates to improve its efficiency and demonstrate its value better. I'll try and allocate it some time this week.

The change is very minor and would be fully reversible in future versions (Go makes no guarantees about object file format that I know of), so I don't know if it counts as a 'proposal'.
